precis:
BONELESS BEEF REMISSION ORDER, 1993 - which provides for the remission of
the 25% surtax on boneless beef imported in 1993 and released by Canada
Customs in 1994 that does not exceed the quota limit specified in the
Surtax on Boneless Beef Order No. 2, 1994.
